WEBVTT

00:01.336 --> 00:04.422
AKU: Long ago,
in a distant land,

00:04.506 --> 00:09.302
I, Aku, the shape-shifting
master of darkness,

00:09.385 --> 00:12.472
unleashed an unspeakable evil.

00:12.889 --> 00:18.561
But a foolish samurai warrior
wielding a magic sword,

00:18.645 --> 00:21.481
stepped forth to oppose me.

00:21.981 --> 00:24.192
(SWORD CLANGING)

00:24.275 --> 00:26.736
Before the final blow
was struck,

00:26.819 --> 00:29.239
I tore open a portal in time

00:29.322 --> 00:33.826
and flung him into the future,
where my evil is law.

00:34.244 --> 00:38.331
Now the fool seeks to return
to the past

00:38.414 --> 00:42.835
