04:17.049 --> 04:18.050
JACK: Father?

04:18.926 --> 04:19.927
Mother?

04:38.863 --> 04:41.073
(FIRE CRACKLING)

04:41.157 --> 04:42.742
Not too smart, is it?

04:43.117 --> 04:46.788
Going out into a blizzard
With just a funny robe and sandals?

04:47.246 --> 04:49.749
You could catch
your death out there or, worse.

04:49.999 --> 04:52.001
The storm should pass by tomorrow.

04:52.460 --> 04:54.045
You can rest here till then.

04:54.754 --> 04:57.381
Here. This will give you
your strength back.

04:57.757 --> 04:58.758
Thank you.

04:58.966 --> 05:00.301
You are very kind.

05:00.718 --> 05:03.638
It's okay.
Just be careful next time.

05:03.930 --> 05:05.973
That weather out there is no joke.

05:06.432 --> 05:09.435
We've been mining up here
for the last five years.

05:09.685 --> 05:13.523
We've managed to mine
these three priceless stones.

05:13.856 --> 05:17.860
One more, we can retire
and leave this blasted mountain.

05:18.152 --> 05:20.571
Will you stop with
the showing off?

05:21.113 --> 05:23.991
Pretty soon, the whole mountain's
gonna know about those.

05:25.201 --> 05:27.119
No need to worry, my friends.

05:27.620 --> 05:29.497
Your secret is safe with me.

05:30.581 --> 05:32.291
I owe you both my life.

05:32.750 --> 05:35.002
What's with your hand there?

05:35.711 --> 05:37.171
I don't know.

05:41.133 --> 05:42.134
It will not come off.

05:44.637 --> 05:46.097
MAN 1: You better get some rest.

05:52.144 --> 05:54.313
MAN 2: You sure you don't need anything?

05:54.897 --> 05:56.524
No. Thank you.

05:56.899 --> 05:58.150
I will be fine.

05:58.818 --> 05:59.986
Brave kid.

06:00.444 --> 06:02.196
Not too smart, but, brave.

06:04.657 --> 06:06.617
It is still very cold.

06:14.458 --> 06:15.835
MAN: Help!

06:18.296 --> 06:19.505
Help!

06:20.631 --> 06:21.716
(WEAKLY) Help...

06:22.341 --> 06:23.843
He-elp.

06:24.552 --> 06:25.595
JACK: Can I help you?

06:25.803 --> 06:27.638
Boy, am I glad to see you.

06:27.722 --> 06:29.557
I thought I'd never get out of here.

06:29.974 --> 06:32.184
There I was, just checking out the view,

06:32.268 --> 06:33.978
and it is beautiful,
mind you,

06:34.061 --> 06:37.481
when suddenly the floor started
to give way beneath me.

06:37.857 --> 06:40.484
Luckily, this rope... (SCREAMING)

06:44.614 --> 06:45.615
Are you okay?

06:46.157 --> 06:48.284
I'm fine.
How are you doing?

06:48.367 --> 06:50.244
I am sorry.
Must have slipped.

06:50.828 --> 06:53.497
No problem.
Don't even worry about it.

06:54.206 --> 06:56.292
But, if you could pull me up soon,

06:56.375 --> 06:57.752
that would be good, too.

06:58.002 --> 06:59.086
And why should I?

06:59.545 --> 07:01.005
What's in it for me, huh?

07:01.881 --> 07:03.716
Uh, I'll give you anything you want.

07:03.799 --> 07:06.093
Just don't drop me, please.

07:06.427 --> 07:08.638
Drop you? I will save you.

07:08.721 --> 07:09.722
Huh?

07:10.431 --> 07:13.351
Okay, so what do you want?

07:13.684 --> 07:14.977
JACK: I do not want anything.

07:15.937 --> 07:17.563
Except everything you've got.

07:17.897 --> 07:20.691
I will accept nothing
for only doing what is right.

07:20.983 --> 07:23.235
You're gonna pay,
or, I shall drop you.

07:23.444 --> 07:25.696
No, do not worry.
I will pull you up.

07:26.113 --> 07:28.658
Come on.
Give me some money.

07:29.033 --> 07:31.327
Please, we must hurry
before the rope breaks.

07:31.744 --> 07:34.288
Uh, you know, never mind.

07:34.372 --> 07:37.124
I... I think I'm just
going to stay here for a while

07:37.208 --> 07:39.460
and check out
the view some more.

07:40.044 --> 07:41.045
Are you certain?

07:41.128 --> 07:43.464
Oh, um, yeah.

07:44.131 --> 07:46.133
JACK: Very well,
if that is what you desire.

07:49.011 --> 07:51.055
But, it's pretty stupid,
if you ask me.

07:57.144 --> 07:58.312
(SNIFFS)

