(GROANS)

08:01.315 --> 08:03.693
(COUGHING)

08:20.418 --> 08:22.044
(GROANS)

08:55.077 --> 08:56.704
(BARKING)

09:01.667 --> 09:03.127
(CROWS CAWING)

09:06.964 --> 09:10.176
(BEEPING)

09:22.772 --> 09:23.939
I think

09:24.899 --> 09:25.900
you

09:25.983 --> 09:27.651
owe me an apology.

09:29.403 --> 09:30.488
I said,

09:31.447 --> 09:33.616
you owe me an apology.

09:34.533 --> 09:36.494
(BEEPING)

09:36.577 --> 09:38.662
I'm gonna give you until
the count of three.

09:38.746 --> 09:40.289
(BEEPING)

09:40.372 --> 09:41.373
One.

09:43.334 --> 09:44.585
Two.

09:44.668 --> 09:46.212
(BEEPING)

09:46.295 --> 09:47.296
Three.

10:04.188 --> 10:06.065
(ZAPPING)

10:09.860 --> 10:12.279
(COUGHING)

10:17.368 --> 10:19.078
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

10:24.375 --> 10:25.668
(GROANS)

10:26.544 --> 10:27.711
I feel so...

10:28.879 --> 10:29.880
I feel...

10:31.382 --> 10:32.883
(IN AKU'S VOICE) ...stronger!

10:33.217 --> 10:35.386
Aah! No! No!

10:35.469 --> 10:36.720
This cannot be happening.

10:37.179 --> 10:38.722
Oh, yes, it can.

10:39.348 --> 10:40.516
(GROANS)

10:40.891 --> 10:42.852
Must keep control.

10:43.352 --> 10:45.479
Yeah! Got to get a grip.

10:45.980 --> 10:46.981
(GROANS)

10:47.189 --> 10:48.482
(GRUNTS)

10:48.607 --> 10:49.608
Need help.

10:49.817 --> 10:51.193
The monks. I...

10:51.360 --> 10:55.364
I've got to find those accursed monks.

10:55.573 --> 10:57.074
(GROANING)

10:57.491 --> 10:58.826
JACK: Must find...

11:29.607 --> 11:31.358
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

11:31.483 --> 11:32.484
Yes?

11:32.902 --> 11:33.903
I am Jack.

11:33.986 --> 11:35.070
Oh, yes.

11:35.571 --> 11:38.407
We have been awaiting
your arrival for many days.

11:38.616 --> 11:41.785
The master was worried
an ill fate had befallen you.

11:42.578 --> 11:43.579
Please, this way.

12:10.439 --> 12:11.440
Master Ning,

12:11.774 --> 12:14.235
I am sorry to disturb
your meditation,

12:14.318 --> 12:16.445
But, Jack,
he has arrived.

12:22.993 --> 12:25.955
Ah, yes, the wandering Samurai.

12:26.288 --> 12:27.915
We were worried about you.

12:28.123 --> 12:31.210
We began to wonder if your quest
had ended.

12:31.710 --> 12:34.129
But, we are glad you are with us now.

12:34.463 --> 12:36.757
Again, we extend our invitation.

12:37.299 --> 12:40.886
We believe the pool of convergence
may be of use to you.

12:41.220 --> 12:44.807
All factors of time
and existence converge here

12:45.099 --> 12:47.726
and form
an inter-dimensional nexus,

12:47.810 --> 12:50.437
which we gaze into to study

12:50.521 --> 12:53.607
the infinite facets of reality.

12:54.233 --> 12:56.860
We have never attempted
a physical journey,

12:57.278 --> 12:58.904
but, with proper conditioning,

12:58.988 --> 13:01.865
you would be able
to step into this crossroads

13:01.949 --> 13:04.493
and find your way home.

13:05.160 --> 13:06.328
(GRUNTS)

13:06.412 --> 13:08.497
You seem weary,
brother Jack.

13:08.580 --> 13:09.581
Come.

13:09.665 --> 13:12.126
The purity of our spring
will refresh you.

13:12.418 --> 13:14.003
Come, come.

13:14.086 --> 13:15.587
Tell us of your quest.

13:15.671 --> 13:17.715
What is it you seek?

13:20.759 --> 13:21.760
I...

13:23.178 --> 13:24.179
I seek...

13:30.644 --> 13:34.398
I seek to foil the Samurai,

13:35.399 --> 13:38.819
to destroy his dream of returning home,

13:39.361 --> 13:43.157
and to destroy all
who stand in my way.

13:44.616 --> 13:45.617
No!

13:45.701 --> 13:47.411
(LAUGHING SINISTERLY)

13:49.663 --> 13:50.998
Brothers, the pool!

13:54.626 --> 13:55.627
Huh?

14:08.640 --> 14:12.144
Ah, yes, slaughtering pathetic whelps

14:12.227 --> 14:15.898
is the perfect way to loosen up

14:15.981 --> 14:18.025
before I really

14:20.861 --> 14:22.237
desecrate things.

14:22.321 --> 14:24.114
(SWORD CLANGING)

14:50.182 --> 14:51.809
Aah!

15:05.155 --> 15:06.698
Aah!

15:10.577 --> 15:12.913
(LAUGHING SINISTERLY)

15:14.456 --> 15:16.959
(MONKS YELLING)

15:21.088 --> 15:22.589
(ALL GRUNT)

15:26.844 --> 15:29.763
(GROANING)

15:31.682 --> 15:33.100
(SWORD CLANGING)

15:35.561 --> 15:37.396
(YELLS)

15:40.482 --> 15:41.483
Stop!

15:56.331 --> 16:00.127
(LAUGHING SINISTERLY)

16:02.754 --> 16:03.797
Huh?

16:04.548 --> 16:06.467
(SCREAMING)

16:07.885 --> 16:10.554
(MOANING)

16:17.561 --> 16:18.770
Forgive me.

16:22.983 --> 16:24.568
Be strong, my son.

16:24.860 --> 16:26.236
You are gravely ill.

16:26.445 --> 16:30.199
Aku's very essence
is creeping through your veins,

16:30.282 --> 16:31.867
possessing your body,

16:31.950 --> 16:33.577
poisoning your mind.

16:33.702 --> 16:36.830
It means to devour your spirit.

16:36.997 --> 16:37.998
Please...

16:39.041 --> 16:40.042
Help me.

16:41.335 --> 16:42.419
I beg you.

16:44.630 --> 16:45.631
(MONKS CHANTING)

16:45.714 --> 16:49.593
We are doing what we can
to stave the illness of the flesh,

16:49.843 --> 16:52.429
but we can only slow the sickness.

16:52.804 --> 16:55.933
You have been infected by pure evil,

16:56.016 --> 16:59.686
which can only be purged
by the light of good,

16:59.770 --> 17:01.813
the good within you.

17:01.897 --> 17:04.149
I...

17:04.650 --> 17:05.817
I cannot.

17:06.860 --> 17:09.154
You must help me.

17:09.530 --> 17:10.739
MASTER NING: I am sorry.

17:11.156 --> 17:15.577
This is a sickness
only you can truly cure.

17:16.078 --> 17:18.413
No.

17:18.664 --> 17:20.582
You must. You...

17:22.834 --> 17:25.295
You worthless, wrinkled grub.

17:25.754 --> 17:28.799
I'll have you for dinner, you worm.

17:29.132 --> 17:31.802
I'll eat every last monk
in this hole.

17:32.177 --> 17:34.054
I'll devour you all

17:34.137 --> 17:36.974
just as I have consumed
the Samurai.

17:37.599 --> 17:40.269
(LAUGHING SINISTERLY)

17:41.311 --> 17:42.980
JACK: Cannot fight it.

17:44.064 --> 17:45.190
Not alone.

17:46.483 --> 17:48.569
Cannot do it alone.

17:48.986 --> 17:51.863
MOTHER:
You are not alone, my son.

17:53.156 --> 17:56.243
We are always with you here...

17:56.493 --> 17:58.203
FATHER: Here in your heart...

17:58.996 --> 18:02.249
The place we will make our stand
against this evil.

18:02.666 --> 18:05.419
But, I was not there for you.

18:05.669 --> 18:06.670
Nonsense.

18:07.379 --> 18:09.715
Aku's victories are not your failures.

18:10.215 --> 18:12.843
The struggle against Aku
is arduous,

18:12.926 --> 18:16.555
and none have fought
more bravely than you, my son.

18:16.888 --> 18:19.266
MOTHER: You have won
many victories,

18:19.349 --> 18:23.186
rekindling hope in the hearts
of those you have protected.

18:23.729 --> 18:25.564
Each sends their blessing.

18:29.151 --> 18:30.861
FATHER: Each blessing,

18:30.944 --> 18:33.113
a stone to fortify this land.

18:40.704 --> 18:43.415
Your castle is strong, my son.

18:43.957 --> 18:45.667
MOTHER: Your allies are many.

18:49.504 --> 18:51.506
Wield what lies within

18:53.342 --> 18:55.302
and reclaim what is yours.

18:58.513 --> 19:01.141
Break this siege of darkness.

19:09.816 --> 19:11.234
(LIGHTNING ZAPPING)

19:14.613 --> 19:17.199
(HEROIC INSTRUMENTAL MUSIC PLAYING)

19:49.272 --> 19:51.274
(SINISTER LAUGHTER)

19:56.905 --> 19:59.241
(MONSTERS YELLING)

20:06.289 --> 20:07.833
(SCREAMING)

20:12.879 --> 20:15.841
(SCREAMING)

20:23.807 --> 20:26.101
(SIZZLING)

20:32.023 --> 20:33.150
(SLURPS)

20:33.900 --> 20:35.152
Master Ning,

20:35.986 --> 20:37.404
how can you forgive one

20:37.487 --> 20:39.531
who has raised his sword
against you

20:40.073 --> 20:42.284
and defiled your sanctuary so?

20:42.451 --> 20:45.829
Although, the pool of convergence
is destroyed,

20:45.912 --> 20:47.706
the Nexus still exists.

20:48.290 --> 20:51.209
In time,
we will reconstruct the gateway.

20:51.793 --> 20:52.794
As for you,

20:53.336 --> 20:55.964
had you not defeated
the demon within,

20:56.548 --> 20:59.426
it surely would have
destroyed us all.

21:00.135 --> 21:01.887
We owe you our lives.

21:02.262 --> 21:05.557
My son, all debts are paid.

21:08.727 --> 21:09.936
All, but one.

21:12.647 --> 21:15.108
I said, get off your fat <i>tochis</i>

21:15.233 --> 21:17.611
